{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM04_ST3_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x48,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "It's been a while since I collected these, but they haven't dried up or withered yet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "These flowers are so mysterious...but now's not the time to admire them. I need to see what they're made of."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I'm gonna try grinding them down to extract their elements. Let's see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh right, I need to use that vessel, too. Hmm, I wonder how I'm supposed to use it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keith should've told me exactly how to use it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "As long as the flower doesn't have a will of its own, or act like a medium..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I should be able to figure out how it works by examining its elements. For example..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I hope I'm wrong, but it might've had hallucinogenic elements that only made me see Nio...and other stuff."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "But that couldn't be it. Mr. Keith and Regina both saw Nio, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I think it's safe to conclude that Nio just appears at places that have glowing flowers."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "So, they must all share a common element..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'm gonna do my best on this analysis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Water, fiber, nectar, medicinal properties... So, all that's left after extracting that is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "...What is this? It seems like some kind of essential oil, but that's all I can tell for now!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I don't know how to use the vessel, so I'll just use it like a container."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Ugh...I feel like I'm on the right track, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "At this rate, I bet Mr. Keith would laugh‐no, he'd probably get mad at me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Oh, the liquid's changing color...! Is that because of the vessel!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Huh? It has a comforting aroma. It's almost nostalgic..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? I'm suddenly feeling sleepy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc7,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "No, no, I can't fall asleep...until I finish this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc9,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Zzz...zzz..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...Sis...Sis..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*yawn* ...Oh, Nio...sorry, I fell asleep."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wait, Nio!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "H-How'd...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Something smelled nice."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I was wondering what it was, so I followed it here and found you sleeping..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yay! I didn't know if I'd be able to see you, Nio!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Me, too. Sorry, Sis, I know you've been really worried about me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*sniff* *sniff* It's okay. You don't have to apologize to me, Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I'm just happy to see you! A few times, I thought...that maybe I'd never get to see you again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Come to think of it...where are we? Why are we floating like clouds?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I don't know. Before I even knew it, I was here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I've been feeling...like I can't tell if I'm asleep or awake this whole time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I've tried to remember, but every time I do, my head starts to hurt..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Nio, you don't have to force yourself to remember..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No, no, I'll try harder! I can't let you go to all this trouble by yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "That day, I was picking medicinal herbs to help you out..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But I tried to pick a flower that I saw sticking out of the cliff...and I slipped..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Before I realized it, I was in a place that I don't even know how to describe."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sis...what happened to me...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's okay. Everything will be okay, Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We can talk to each other, so now I just have to figure out how to bring you back from here!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "So...please wait a little longer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...Really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Of course. When your big sis says she'll do something, she's gonna do it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'll be waiting! Cuz Sis never lies!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Although, she is a little too easygoing and unreliable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Th-That's not true. I've been able to do everything by myself recently."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, are you sure? Can you wake yourself up in the morning?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Can you keep yourself from collapsing because you're so busy synthesizing, you forget to eat?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x34,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I-I'm fiiine... I haven't done that...too often."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x35,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Your workshop... I miss it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x36,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Pana's there, and Ernie stops by sometimes, and the cauldron  is always simmering..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x37,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ernie... That reminds me! Nio, these are for you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x38,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, these are the candies that Ernie always brings!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x39,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I've been carrying them around in case I saw you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yay! I love these!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I wanna go home...to your workshop..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Don't cry, Nio. For sure, I will‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What was that!? It felt like I just got shocked..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sis...! I have to go back to that place..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Nio, wait!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3e,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x40,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Protection mechanism...deficiency...<CR>Severe blockage...to the directional<CR>transmission system...has occurred..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3e,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x41,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Forced termination...of command...<CR>Switching to...dormant status..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x42,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Nio!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x43,
            "msg_string": "...Was it a dream?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x44,
            "msg_string": "No, it couldn't be a dream! I can still feel Nio's touch...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x79,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x45,
            "msg_string": "I need to hurry! Nio is waiting for me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You lost one Pouch of Candy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You got Flower Oil."
        }
    ]
}